

Character

4 elements, 5 skills for each, mapped to 1-5 (or user set)
Can change gender as usual
Level-up allows upgrading of skills. 1 skill point a level? Different skill effects at higher levels.

Saving

Save game as xml file. when game is loaded level data is loaded from file, then overwritten by data from save file.
Character level and skills and upgrades saved at top. Also the current level
Then data for each level saved under their own subheadings.
Entire save file loaded into memory, then the relevant parts editted and then entire thing written back into the file replacing the old one.

Scenes

Box that when entering starts scene. Player dropped vertically down to ground at this point. Game zooms in to the scene location.
Scene special scene entity, with width, height and dialogue sequence in memory.

